- This is a secure and scalable configuration management service that automates
  the process of keeping your amazon ec2 and hybrid infrastructure in a state that you define

BENEFITS OF STATE MANAGER TO MY ORGANIZATION

- Bootstrap instances with specific software at start up
- Download and update agents on a defined schedule, including the ssm agent
- configure network settings
- Patch instances with software updates throughout their lifecyle
- Run scripts on linux, macos and windows managed instances throughout their
  lifecycle

ASSOCIATION

- This is a configuration that is assigned to your managed instances.
- The configuration defines the state that you want to maintain on your instances
- The association specifies a schedule for when the configuration is applied once or
  reapplied at specified times.
